    "description": "Zostel Asia Pacific Associates, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a SEO Specialist for our Navi Mumbai operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Zostel Asia Pacific Associates:\nZostel Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zostel Asia Pacific Associates!",
